---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="落地场景 — AEROS" description="智能仓储、移动操作、商业服务机器人、机器人 OEM——看 AEROS 怎么落地。" lang="zh">

  <section class="section" style="padding-bottom: var(--space-2xl);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">落地场景</div>
      <h1 class="page-title">AEROS 跑在哪里</h1>
      <p class="page-desc">
        凡是需要智能体长期运行、安全进化、行为可追溯的场景，都是 AEROS 的战场。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Use Case 1: Warehousing ═══ -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="usecase">
        <div class="usecase-info">
          <div class="usecase-tag">智能仓储</div>
          <h2 class="usecase-title">一套运行时，<br>管一整个车队</h2>

          <div class="pain-point">
            <span class="pain-label">痛点</span>
            <p>仓库里 20-50 台机器人，AMR、协作臂、分拣机，每台一套软件栈。能力不能跨形态复用，出了问题没有审计链路可以追。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="aeros-value">
            <span class="value-label">AEROS 方案</span>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>统一运行时</strong>——一个生命周期管理器搞定整个车队</li>
              <li><strong>ECM 跨形态复用</strong>——写一次能力，到处部署</li>
              <li><strong>全链路审计</strong>——每个决策、每次行动都可追溯</li>
              <li><strong>安全门部署</strong>——新能力必须过安全检查才能上线</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="usecase-visual">
          <div class="fleet-diagram">
            <div class="fleet-header">
              <span class="fleet-name">warehouse-east</span>
              <span class="fleet-status">12 agents &middot; all governed</span>
            </div>
            <div class="fleet-agents">
              <div class="fleet-agent">
                <span class="agent-type">AMR</span>
                <span class="agent-count">&times;6</span>
                <span class="agent-ecm">nav, obstacle-avoidance</span>
              </div>
              <div class="fleet-agent">
                <span class="agent-type">Arm</span>
                <span class="agent-count">&times;4</span>
                <span class="agent-ecm">pick-place, dual-grasp</span>
              </div>
              <div class="fleet-agent">
                <span class="agent-type">Sorter</span>
                <span class="agent-count">&times;2</span>
                <span class="agent-ecm">classify, route</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="fleet-footer">
              <span>Governance: <strong style="color: var(--success)">strict</strong></span>
              <span>Uptime: 14d 3h</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Use Case 2: Mobile Manipulation ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="usecase usecase--reverse">
        <div class="usecase-info">
          <div class="usecase-tag">移动操作</div>
          <h2 class="usecase-title">导航、感知、操作<br>——一个运行时管到底</h2>

          <div class="pain-point">
            <span class="pain-label">痛点</span>
            <p>移动操作机器人同时跑导航、感知和操作三套子系统，传统做法各自独立，没有统一的生命周期和故障处理。一个挂了，其他的不知道。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="aeros-value">
            <span class="value-label">AEROS 方案</span>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>统一运行时</strong>——导航 + 感知 + 操作共享一个生命周期管理器</li>
              <li><strong>跨能力监控</strong>——Watcher 覆盖整个感知→决策→执行链路</li>
              <li><strong>结构化恢复</strong>——操作失败时，导航和感知优雅降级</li>
              <li><strong>受控进化</strong>——升级一个能力，不搞崩其他的</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="usecase-visual">
          <div class="fleet-diagram">
            <div class="fleet-header">
              <span class="fleet-name">mobile-manip-fleet</span>
              <span class="fleet-status">4 agents &middot; lab environment</span>
            </div>
            <div class="fleet-agents">
              <div class="fleet-agent">
                <span class="agent-type">Manipulator</span>
                <span class="agent-count">&times;2</span>
                <span class="agent-ecm">nav, grasp, inspect</span>
              </div>
              <div class="fleet-agent">
                <span class="agent-type">Scout</span>
                <span class="agent-count">&times;1</span>
                <span class="agent-ecm">nav, object-detect</span>
              </div>
              <div class="fleet-agent">
                <span class="agent-type">Supervisor</span>
                <span class="agent-count">&times;1</span>
                <span class="agent-ecm">monitor, coordinate</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="fleet-footer">
              <span>Governance: <strong style="color: var(--success)">strict</strong></span>
              <span>Uptime: 3d 8h</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Use Case 3: Service Robots ═══ -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="usecase">
        <div class="usecase-info">
          <div class="usecase-tag">商业服务</div>
          <h2 class="usecase-title">7x24 不停机，<br>远程管到底</h2>

          <div class="pain-point">
            <span class="pain-label">痛点</span>
            <p>服务机器人在酒店、医院、商场全天候运行。需要组合多种能力、不停机 OTA 升级，法规一变还得远程推策略。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="aeros-value">
            <span class="value-label">AEROS 方案</span>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>ECM 热替换</strong>——不重启 Agent 就能升级能力</li>
              <li><strong>远程策略推送</strong>——治理规则一键下发到整个车队</li>
              <li><strong>金丝雀部署</strong>——新能力先推 5% 的机器人试水</li>
              <li><strong>秒级回滚</strong>——出问题一秒回退</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="usecase-visual">
          <div class="fleet-diagram">
            <div class="fleet-header">
              <span class="fleet-name">hotel-fleet-shenzhen</span>
              <span class="fleet-status">8 agents &middot; 3 locations</span>
            </div>
            <div class="fleet-agents">
              <div class="fleet-agent">
                <span class="agent-type">Concierge</span>
                <span class="agent-count">&times;3</span>
                <span class="agent-ecm">greet, navigate, deliver</span>
              </div>
              <div class="fleet-agent">
                <span class="agent-type">Room Service</span>
                <span class="agent-count">&times;3</span>
                <span class="agent-ecm">elevator, deliver, return</span>
              </div>
              <div class="fleet-agent">
                <span class="agent-type">Security</span>
                <span class="agent-count">&times;2</span>
                <span class="agent-ecm">patrol, anomaly-detect</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="fleet-footer">
              <span>Policy update: <strong style="color: var(--primary)">2h ago</strong></span>
              <span>Uptime: 89d</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Use Case 4: OEM ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="usecase usecase--reverse">
        <div class="usecase-info">
          <div class="usecase-tag">机器人 OEM</div>
          <h2 class="usecase-title">做平台，<br>别做项目</h2>

          <div class="pain-point">
            <span class="pain-label">痛点</span>
            <p>每个客户都从头搭运行时。项目之间能力没法复用，治理更是没有。集成成本吃掉利润，说好的平台化永远落不了地。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="aeros-value">
            <span class="value-label">AEROS 方案</span>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>标准运行时</strong>——别再给每个客户重造轮子</li>
              <li><strong>ECM 生态</strong>——能力写一次，跨项目、跨机型复用</li>
              <li><strong>治理即插即用</strong>——企业客户开箱就有审计和策略</li>
              <li><strong>交付提速</strong>——从几个月的定制集成缩短到几周</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="usecase-visual">
          <div class="fleet-diagram">
            <div class="fleet-header">
              <span class="fleet-name">OEM Platform</span>
              <span class="fleet-status">reusable across projects</span>
            </div>
            <div class="fleet-agents">
              <div class="fleet-agent">
                <span class="agent-type">Project A</span>
                <span class="agent-count">Warehouse</span>
                <span class="agent-ecm">shared: nav, pick-place</span>
              </div>
              <div class="fleet-agent">
                <span class="agent-type">Project B</span>
                <span class="agent-count">Hospital</span>
                <span class="agent-ecm">shared: nav, deliver</span>
              </div>
              <div class="fleet-agent">
                <span class="agent-type">Project C</span>
                <span class="agent-count">Retail</span>
                <span class="agent-ecm">shared: nav, greet</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="fleet-footer">
              <span>ECMs reused: <strong style="color: var(--success)">12 / 18</strong></span>
              <span>Dev time: -60%</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ CTA ═══ -->
  <section class="section" style="text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">聊聊你的场景</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin: 0 auto var(--space-xl);">
        预约一次 Demo，我们来看看 AEROS 怎么适配你的车队、硬件和治理需求。
      </p>
      <a href="/zh/contact" class="btn btn-primary">预约 Demo</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  .page-desc {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 520px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .section-alt {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  /* ═══ Use Case Layout ═══ */
  .usecase {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .usecase--reverse .usecase-info { order: 2; }
  .usecase--reverse .usecase-visual { order: 1; }

  .usecase-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  .usecase-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .pain-point, .aeros-value {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
  .pain-label, .value-label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  .pain-label { color: var(--warning); }
  .value-label { color: var(--success); }

  .pain-point p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--warning);
  }
  .aeros-value ul {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }
  .aeros-value li {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding-left: var(--space-md);
    position: relative;
  }
  .aeros-value li::before {
    content: '\2713';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--success);
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  .aeros-value strong { color: var(--text-primary); }

  /* ═══ Fleet Diagram ═══ */
  .fleet-diagram {
    background: #0D1117;
    border: 1px solid #21262D;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .fleet-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    background: #161B22;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #21262D;
  }
  .fleet-name { color: #F0F6FC; font-weight: 500; }
  .fleet-status { color: #8B949E; font-size: 12px; }

  .fleet-agents {
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }
  .fleet-agent {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto auto 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-sm) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #21262D;
    color: #C9D1D9;
  }
  .fleet-agent:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .agent-type { color: #F0F6FC; font-weight: 500; }
  .agent-count { color: #8B949E; }
  .agent-ecm { color: #8B949E; font-size: 12px; }

  .fleet-footer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    border-top: 1px solid #21262D;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #8B949E;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .usecase {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .usecase--reverse .usecase-info,
    .usecase--reverse .usecase-visual {
      order: unset;
    }
  }
</style>
